  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>English version now available!</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[TellTale - Casino Murder Case]</strong> is a <u><strong>full-voice</strong></u> indie <u><strong>mystery game</strong></u> featuring youngest lawyer, Kang Ho-yeon, who reveals the truth about the casino murder case and achieves innocence at trial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/c5ac96404b90625ec04715c2882b0ace.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/c5ac96404b90625ec04715c2882b0ace.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/bfac44d40edd749f9b3915b7592589c6.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/bfac44d40edd749f9b3915b7592589c6.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player must become the lawyer in charge of the casino murder case and get to the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigation Part - go to the casino, the site of the murder, and investigate and collect evidence. <br>Trial Part - defend the accused in the trial with evidence obtained from the investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the various mystery mini-games offered during this process, players can experience reasoning from multiple angles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery Theater</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"NG! There's a contradiction hidden in the witness's theater!\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/0bd07352fa7c7c7b7a110bb23e373f49.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/0bd07352fa7c7c7b7a110bb23e373f49.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery Theater is a mini-game that points out contradictions in the testimony of witnesses embodied as theaters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/125ae1e1a045983ed6473bfe6347c6e6.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/125ae1e1a045983ed6473bfe6347c6e6.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/125ae1e1a045983ed6473bfe6347c6e6.mp4?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the mystery theater begins, the contents of the testimony are played in animation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The scene is a testimony claiming to have attacked the victim's left face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/598e471d4ba315262dd8524398a1a804.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/598e471d4ba315262dd8524398a1a804.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At this point, the player may find a contradiction in the detective notebook based on a \"right skull fracture\" written on the autopsy record.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a result, you can press the NG button and submit the corresponding evidence to get the answer and question the witness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Choice</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/184e29a996061d4fd6bf289dd792473c.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/184e29a996061d4fd6bf289dd792473c.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Choice is a game in which four responses are selected and answered to the witness's testimony in real-time: \"Positive, Negative, Interrogation, and Silence.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/7e3566184ea7870d04200a1ee7bc6fbc.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/7e3566184ea7870d04200a1ee7bc6fbc.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each choice was based on a nonverbal expression. For example, the affirmation swipes up and down the screen as if nodding, and the negation swipes from side to side as if turning heads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your quickness to enjoy psychological warfare with witnesses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-Examination</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/f62a912c0f4c9942da71d892b4992751.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/f62a912c0f4c9942da71d892b4992751.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-examination is a mini-game that simultaneously interrogates two witnesses who make different claims.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/9ac748acda68d0bfddd5e1d0d60152e2.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/9ac748acda68d0bfddd5e1d0d60152e2.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the game begins, both witnesses testify as they claim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player selects a pair of contradictory testimonies and presses the cross button.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/42db2eda7a829789fc5b72800a935b22.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/42db2eda7a829789fc5b72800a935b22.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character interrogates the content pointed out at the intersection, and the two witnesses correct the pointed testimony, respectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player continues the cross-examination, including the newly revised testimony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/66ee04af3c6aebf8fccaabdb09cecbf0.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/66ee04af3c6aebf8fccaabdb09cecbf0.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/baef0a6e6200d4113c1dcd4b44cf1475.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/baef0a6e6200d4113c1dcd4b44cf1475.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[TellTale] features a total of 10 unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players investigate the incident, find out the interests of those involved, and uncover hidden secrets.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>English version now available!</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[TellTale - Casino Murder Case]</strong> is a <u><strong>full-voice</strong></u> indie <u><strong>mystery game</strong></u> featuring youngest lawyer, Kang Ho-yeon, who reveals the truth about the casino murder case and achieves innocence at trial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/c5ac96404b90625ec04715c2882b0ace.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/c5ac96404b90625ec04715c2882b0ace.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/bfac44d40edd749f9b3915b7592589c6.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/bfac44d40edd749f9b3915b7592589c6.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player must become the lawyer in charge of the casino murder case and get to the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigation Part - go to the casino, the site of the murder, and investigate and collect evidence. <br>Trial Part - defend the accused in the trial with evidence obtained from the investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the various mystery mini-games offered during this process, players can experience reasoning from multiple angles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mystery Theater</p></li></ul><p class=\