_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/598e471d4ba315262dd8524398a1a804.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At this point, the player may find a contradiction in the detective notebook based on a \"right skull fracture\" written on the autopsy record.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a result, you can press the NG button and submit the corresponding evidence to get the answer and question the witness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Choice</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/184e29a996061d4fd6bf289dd792473c.avif?t=1733372236\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras_big/184e29a996061d4fd6bf289dd792473c.avif?t=1733372236 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Choice is a game in which four responses are selected and answered to the witness's testimony in real-time: \"Positive, Negative, Interrogation, and Silence.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/7e3566184ea7870d04200a1ee7bc6fbc.poster.avif?t=1733372236\" width=720 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204030/extras/7e3566184ea7870d04200a1ee7bc6fbc.webm?t=1733372236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each choice was based on a nonverbal expression. For example, the affirmation swipes up and down the screen as if nodding, and the negation swipes from side to side as if turning heads.</p><